    "pdp_imageblockcontent_3zi4AL": {
      "type": "pdp-imageblockcontent",
      "settings": {
        "textarea_measurement_bm": "<ol>\n    <li>Breathable Quilted Cover\n        <span class=\"caption\">\n            made to be naturally soft, long-lasting and breathable.\n        <\/span>\n<br>\n        Add Celliant Infused Cover (optional) <span class=\"caption\"> with Sleep Recover Technology™ to regulate body temperature and promote recovery and well-being.<\/span>\n    <\/li>\n    <li>Cooling Gel Memory Foam\n        <span class=\"caption\">\ndraws away unwanted body heat and provides improved spinal alignment for a more comfortable sleep.        <\/span>\n    <\/li>\n    <li>Bear Dynamic Foam\n        <span class=\"caption\">\noffers balanced support and deeper compression for better pressure relief.        <\/span>\n    <\/li>\n    <li>High-Density Support Foam\n        <span class=\"caption\">\n            provides long-lasting durability\n        <\/span>\n    <\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h5><a class=\"btn btn-white shadow\" href=\"\/pages\/compare\">Compare Features<\/a><\/h5>",
        "bottom_text": "Looking for a specific firmness? Check out our firmness guide.",
        "bottom_link": "\/pages\/firmness-guide"
      }
    },
    "pdp_bear_original_hybrid_features_ad4dAm": {
      "type": "pdp-bear-original-hybrid-features",
      "blocks": {
        "2ac9d728-3a6f-4b9c-a784-b75d9edbb258": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "All-Foam Mattress Feel",
            "description": "<p>An all-foam mattress gives your body a unique level of support, aiding in spinal alignment and hugging your body no matter your favorite sleep position. Plus, this is the best option if you or your partner need the best reduced motion transfer.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "4563ed6a-c31c-4cef-88f5-307e82dc0a9e": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Hybrid Mattress Feel",
            "description": "<p>A hybrid mattress uses innerspring coils, so you’re getting that tried-and-true support, deeper compression, and classic responsive bounce of a traditional mattress. The foam component offers comfort through a hugging sensation. <\/p>"
          }
        },
        "300b27a5-fa44-4024-a0dd-2e9f6268b927": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Contouring Memory Foam",
            "description": "<p>Both the all-foam and hybrid mattresses have two top layers of cooling, gel memory foam. These comfort layers help to draw away body heat, relieve pressure on the hips and shoulders while filling in the nooks and crannies of your back and body.<\/p>"
          }
        },
        "e86436fb-fd23-476f-b714-7d64bdaba667": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Sleeping Cool Through The Night",
            "description": "<p>For sleepers who are prone to getting hot at night, the hybrid model can offer more breathability. Air can more easily flow through the coils of the hybrid mattress, so for some this increased breathability might be important. Plus, both options have heat reducing gel memory foam for added comfort. <\/p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "2ac9d728-3a6f-4b9c-a784-b75d9edbb258",
